'''埃洛伊·亞圖洛·席曼尼茲·索拉諾'''（{{lang-es|Eloy Arturo Jiménez Solano}}，{{bd|1996年|11月27日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的外野手，目前效力於芝加哥白襪。
==職業生涯==
===芝加哥小熊===
2013年7月，席曼尼茲以280萬美元的國際簽約金加盟小熊隊。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.cubs.mlb.com/news/article/52594736/|title=Chicago Cubs set to sign top international outfielder prospect Eloy Jimenez|work=Chicago Cubs|accessdate=November 19, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304121832/http://m.cubs.mlb.com/news/article/52594736/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://voices.suntimes.com/sports/inside-the-cubs/cubs-appear-to-have-top-latin-prospects-signged/|title=Chicago Sun-Times - Chicago : News : Politics : Things To Do : Sports|work=Chicago|accessdate=November 19, 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150628113001/http://voices.suntimes.com/sports/inside-the-cubs/cubs-appear-to-have-top-latin-prospects-signged/|archivedate=2015-06-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/international/cubs-sign-no-1-international-prospect-eloy-jimenez/|title=Cubs Sign No. 1 International Prospect Eloy Jimenez|work=BaseballAmerica.com|accessdate=November 19, 2015|archive-date=2017-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170705042326/http://www.baseballamerica.com/international/cubs-sign-no-1-international-prospect-eloy-jimenez/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.cubs.mlb.com/news/article/62992920/|title=Top prospects Eloy Jimenez, Gleybar Torres growing, learning with Cubs|work=Chicago Cubs|accessdate=November 19, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304101950/http://m.cubs.mlb.com/news/article/62992920/|dead-url=no}}</ref>當時大聯盟給了席曼尼茲「五拍子球員」的高評價。<ref>{{cite web|title = 2013 Prospect Watch|url = http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/prospects/watch/y2013/|website = Major League Baseball|access-date = February 8, 2016|archive-date = 2013-07-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130729051727/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/prospects/watch/y2013/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

2014年，席曼尼茲開啟職業生涯。那年他的上壘率僅2成68，而且還因傷提前結束球季。<ref>{{cite web|title = Chicago Cubs Top 20 Prospects for 2015|url = http://www.minorleagueball.com/2014/12/7/7351045/chicago-cubs-top-20-prospects-for-2015|website = Minor League Ball|access-date = February 8, 2016|first = John|last = Sickels|archive-date = 2020-11-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201111180435/https://www.minorleagueball.com/2014/12/7/7351045/chicago-cubs-top-20-prospects-for-2015|dead-url = no}}</ref>2015年，球團將他升上1A磨練。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20150702&content_id=134183668&vkey=news_milb&fext=.jsp&sid=milb|title=Chicago Cubs' Eloy Jimenez clubs second homer in two games for Eugene Emeralds - MiLB.com News - The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|work=MiLB.com|accessdate=November 19, 2015|archive-date=2016-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160618132647/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20150702&content_id=134183668&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb&sid=milb|dead-url=no}}</ref>席曼尼茲不僅將上壘率提升至3成28，還敲出7支全壘打。

2016年，他在低階1A繳出3成29打擊率，敲出14轟與81分打點的成績。<ref>{{cite web|title = Cubs Carl Edwards on witnessing 2015 playoffs|url = http://m.cubs.mlb.com/news/article/162156078/cubs-carl-edwards-on-witnessing-2015-playoffs|website = Chicago Cubs|access-date = February 8, 2016|archive-date = 2017-11-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171114075055/http://m.cubs.mlb.com/news/article/162156078/cubs-carl-edwards-on-witnessing-2015-playoffs/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=650391#/career/R/hitting/2016/ALL|title=Eloy Jimenez Stats, Highlights, Bio - MiLB.com Stats - The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|publisher=|accessdate=November 19, 2016|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026083013/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=650391#/career/R/hitting/2016/ALL|dead-url=no}}</ref>於是他在隔年升上高階1A。<ref name="mlb.com1">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/events/afl/club.jsp?team_id=555|title=Major League Baseball - Winter Leagues - Arizona Fall League|publisher=|accessdate=November 19, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108111206/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/events/afl/club.jsp?team_id=555|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===芝加哥白襪===
2017年7月13日，小熊隊用席曼尼茲、Dylan Cease、Matt Rose和Bryant Flete向白襪隊交易[[荷西·昆塔納|荷西·昆塔納]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://chicago.suntimes.com/sports/cubs-acquire-jose-quintana-in-white-sox-trade/|title=Crosstown shocker: Cubs acquire José Quintana from Sox in blockbuster|publisher=|accessdate=March 12, 2018|archive-date=2019-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329051838/https://chicago.suntimes.com/sports/cubs-acquire-jose-quintana-in-white-sox-trade/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而席曼尼茲在季中升上2A。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.milb.com/milb/news/new-no-2-white-sox-prospect-eloy-jimenez-beats-former-team-with-two-run-single/c-242037654/t-185364810 |title=Jimenez makes good first impression on Dash |publisher=MiLB.com |date=July 13, 2017 |accessdate=April 9, 2018 |archive-date=2017-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714075922/https://www.milb.com/milb/news/new-no-2-white-sox-prospect-eloy-jimenez-beats-former-team-with-two-run-single/c-242037654/t-185364810 |dead-url=no }}</ref>這年他的打擊率為3成12，並敲出19轟與65分打點。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=650391#/career/R/hitting/2017/ALL|title=Eloy Jimenez Stats, Highlights, Bio - MiLB.com Stats - The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|publisher=|accessdate=November 19, 2017|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026083013/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=650391#/career/R/hitting/2017/ALL|dead-url=no}}</ref>他也在球季末進入球隊的40人名單。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/sports/white-sox-add-eloy-jimenez-to-40-man-roster/|title=White Sox add Eloy Jimenez to 40-man roster|publisher=|accessdate=March 12, 2018|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622140926/https://chicago.suntimes.com/sports/white-sox-add-eloy-jimenez-to-40-man-roster/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年，儘管他在春訓快結束時膝蓋與胸口受傷，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailyherald.com/sports/20180404/next-wave-of-chicago-white-sox-prospects-to-keep-an-eye-on |title=Next wave of Chicago White Sox prospects to keep an eye on |publisher=Dailyherald.com |date= |accessdate=April 9, 2018 |archive-date=2019-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401203420/https://www.dailyherald.com/sports/20180404/next-wave-of-chicago-white-sox-prospects-to-keep-an-eye-on |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過球團還是在球季中將他升上3A。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/sports/white-sox-promote-eloy-jimenez-to-aaa-charlotte/ |title=White Sox promote Eloy Jimenez to Class AAA Charlotte |publisher=Chicago Sun-Times |date=2018-06-21 |accessdate=2019-10-07 |archive-date=2019-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401192523/https://chicago.suntimes.com/sports/white-sox-promote-eloy-jimenez-to-aaa-charlotte/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>該年他的打擊率為3成37，並敲出22轟與75分打點。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=650391#/career/R/hitting/2018/ALL|title=Eloy Jimenez Stats, Highlights, Bio - MiLB.com Stats - The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|publisher=MiLB.com|accessdate=October 23, 2018|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026083013/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=650391#/career/R/hitting/2018/ALL|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年3月22日，他與球隊簽下6年4300萬美元的合約。這也是美國職棒史上球團端給小聯盟球員的最高薪。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.milb.com/milb/news/chicago-white-sox-sign-eloy-jimenez-to-six-year-43-million-deal/c-305472518 |title=White Sox sign Eloy to six-year contract |publisher=milb.com |accessdate=27 April 2019 |archive-date=2019-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190726022116/https://www.milb.com/milb/news/chicago-white-sox-sign-eloy-jimenez-to-six-year-43-million-deal/c-305472518 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/whitesox/ct-spt-white-sox-eloy-jimenez-contract-details-20190322-story.html |title=Details of Eloy Jimenez's record contract with the White Sox include a $5 million bonus and a potential value of $75M |publisher=chicagotribune.com |accessdate=27 April 2019 |archive-date=2019-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503062526/https://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/whitesox/ct-spt-white-sox-eloy-jimenez-contract-details-20190322-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.si.com/mlb/2019/03/20/eloy-jimenez-contract-white-sox |title=Report: White Sox Agree to Six-Year Deal With Top Prospect Eloy Jimenez |publisher=si.com |accessdate=27 April 2019 |archive-date=2019-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129050827/https://www.si.com/mlb/2019/03/20/eloy-jimenez-contract-white-sox |dead-url=no }}</ref>

這年席曼尼茲成功擠進球隊的25人名單內，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nbcsports.com/chicago/white-sox/white-sox-roster-set-opening-day-and-yes-eloy-jimenez-it-breakdown|title=The White Sox roster is set for Opening Day, and yes, Eloy Jimenez is on it|work=CBS Sports Chicago|accessdate=1 April 2019|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401192551/https://www.nbcsports.com/chicago/white-sox/white-sox-roster-set-opening-day-and-yes-eloy-jimenez-it-breakdown|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過他在4月29日就因腳踝受傷進入傷兵名單。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://sports.yahoo.com/eloy-jimenez-placed-on-10-day-il-with-high-ankle-sprain-153218344.html |title=Eloy Jimenez placed on 10-day IL with high ankle sprain |publisher=Sports.yahoo.com |date=2019-04-28 |accessdate=2019-10-07 |archive-date=2020-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810004521/https://sports.yahoo.com/eloy-jimenez-placed-on-10-day-il-with-high-ankle-sprain-153218344.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>這年他的[[DRS_(棒球)|DRS]]為-11分，是全大聯盟左外野手最低的數據。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=lf&stats=fld&lg=all&qual=y&type=1&season=2019&month=0&season1=2019&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&startdate=2019-01-01&enddate=2019-12-31&sort=13,d |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2019 » Left Fielders » Fielding Statistics | FanGraphs Baseball |publisher=Fangraphs.com |date=2019-01-01 |accessdate=2019-10-07 |archive-date=2021-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210809074308/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=lf&stats=fld&lg=all&qual=y&type=1&season=2019&month=0&season1=2019&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&startdate=2019-01-01&enddate=2019-12-31&sort=13,d |dead-url=no }}</ref>該年他的打擊率為2成67，並敲出31轟與79分打點，在美聯新人王票選上拿下第4名。

